---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="Posts — Power Grab TX">
  <div class="posts-summary">
    <h1>Latest Posts From Power Grab TX</h1>
    <p class="posts-intro">Explore our recent insights on Texas AI data centers and digital infrastructure.</p>

    <div class="posts-grid">

      <div class="post-card">
        <img src="/transforming_texas-.webp" alt="How AI Data Centers Are Transforming Texas" />
        <div class="post-card-body">
          <h2><a href="/posts/transforming-texas">How AI Data Centers Are Transforming Texas</a></h2>
          <p>How AI Data Centers are transforming Texas communities across the state, reshaping local economies, environmental policy, and the reliability of the Texas power grid. As these facilities continue to expand, Texans deserve a clear understanding of all the benefits, all the risks, and long-term implications.</p>
          <a href="/posts/transforming-texas" class="read-more">READ MORE →</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="post-card">
        <img src="/post-featured-image.webp" alt="Billion-Dollar Boom: Texas AI Data Centers in 2026" />
        <div class="post-card-body">
          <h2><a href="/posts/billion-dollar-boom">Billion-Dollar Boom: Texas AI Data Centers in 2026</a></h2>
          <p>Texas is rapidly becoming one of the most important locations in the United States for AI-focused data centers. With abundant land, competitive power markets, and a business-friendly environment, the state is attracting hyperscalers, cloud providers, and enterprise AI operators.</p>
          <a href="/posts/billion-dollar-boom" class="read-more">READ MORE →</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="post-card">
        <img src="/data_centers.webp" alt="Why AI Data Centers Are Exploding in Texas" />
        <div class="post-card-body">
          <h2><a href="/posts/exploding-in-texas">Why AI Data Centers Are Exploding in Texas — And What It Means for the Grid</a></h2>
          <p>Texas AI data centers are expanding at a historic pace in 2026, making the state the epicenter of America's AI infrastructure boom. Over the past three years, the state has seen a surge of new data centers especially the high-density, high-power facilities needed to train and run AI models.</p>
          <a href="/posts/exploding-in-texas" class="read-more">READ MORE →</a>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
<style>
    /* ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
         MOVE TO → src/pages/posts.astro AND src/pages/posts/[slug].astro
         (Split further if post listing vs. single-post styles diverge —
         check which classes are used on which template before moving.)
         ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ */

      .card {
        border: 1px solid #ddd;
        border-radius: 8px;
        padding: 1.2rem;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 0.5rem;
        box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
        transition: box-shadow 0.2s;
      }
      .card:hover {
        box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
      }
      .card hr {
        border: none;
        border-top: 2px solid #ccc;
        margin: 0.4rem 0;
      }
      .card h3 {
        font-size: 1.05rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        line-height: 1.3;
        height: 3.5rem;
        overflow: hidden;
      }
      .card p {
        font-size: 0.95rem;
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: #333;
        height: 21rem;
        overflow: hidden;
      }
      .card ul {
        font-size: 0.92rem;
        line-height: 1.8;
        color: #333;
        padding-left: 1.2rem;
        height: 20rem;
        overflow: hidden;
      }
      .card .learn-more {
        font-size: 0.95rem;
        font-weight: 600;
        color: #1a4a8a;
        display: block;
        margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
      }
      .card .title {
        height: 5.6rem;
        overflow: hidden;
        color: #000080;
        font-weight: 700;
      }
      .card .description {
        font-size: 0.95rem;
        color: #333;
        line-height: 1.6;
        display: -webkit-box;
        -webkit-line-clamp: 5;
        -webkit-box-orient: vertical;
        overflow: hidden;
      }
      .card .provider {
        font-size: 0.88rem;
        color: #1a6a2a;
      }
      .card .readmore {
        font-size: 0.95rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        color: #1a1a1a;
      }
      .cards-section {
        padding: 2rem;
      }
      .cards-section h2 {
        font-size: 1.6rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        text-align: center;
      }
      .posts-section h2 {
        font-size: 1.6rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
      }
      .posts-section {
        padding: 2rem;
        max-width: 1200px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        background: #f4f4f4;
        border-radius: 10px;
      }
      .post-page {
        max-width: 800px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 2rem;
      }
      .post-image {
        width: 100%;
        height: auto;
        border-radius: 10px;
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
      }
      .post-content h1 {
        font-size: 2rem;
        font-weight: 800;
        margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        line-height: 1.3;
      }
      .posts-list .post .date {
        font-size: 0.88rem;
        color: #666;
        margin: 0.2rem 0 0.4rem;
      }
      .posts-list .post p {
        font-size: 0.95rem;
        color: #444;
        line-height: 1.6;
      }
      .post-content h2 {
        font-size: 1.3rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        margin: 2rem 0 0.8rem;
      }
      .post-content h3 {
        font-size: 1.1rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        margin: 1.2rem 0 0.5rem;
      }
      .post-content p {
        font-size: 1rem;
        line-height: 1.8;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
        color: #222;
      }
      .post-related {
        background: #f4f4f4;
        border-radius: 8px;
        padding: 1.2rem 1.5rem;
        margin: 2rem 0;
      }
      .posts-list .post h3 {
        font-size: 1rem;
        font-weight: 600;
      }
      .posts-list .post h3 a {
        color: #1a4a8a;
        font-size: 1rem;
      }
      .post-content ul {
        padding-left: 1.4rem;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
      }
      .post-content ul li {
        font-size: 1rem;
        line-height: 1.8;
        color: #222;
      }
      .post-cta {
        background: #1a3a6a;
        color: #fff;
        padding: 2rem;
        border-radius: 10px;
        margin-top: 2rem;
        text-align: center;
      }
      .post-cta p {
        color: #fff;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
      }
      .post-table {
        width: 100%;
        border-collapse: collapse;
        margin: 1.5rem 0;
      }
      .post-table th {
        background: #1a3a6a;
        color: #fff;
        padding: 0.8rem 1rem;
        text-align: left;
        font-size: 0.95rem;
      }
      .post-table td {
        padding: 0.8rem 1rem;
        border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;
        font-size: 0.95rem;
      }
      .post-table tr:nth-child(even) {
        background: #f4f4f8;
      }
      .posts-summary {
        max-width: 1100px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 2rem;
      }
      .posts-summary h1 {
        font-size: 1.8rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
      }
      .posts-intro {
        font-size: 1rem;
        color: #555;
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
      }
      .posts-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
        gap: 1.5rem;
      }
      @media (max-width: 900px) {
        .posts-grid {
          grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        }
      }
      .post-card {
        border: 1px solid #ddd;
        border-radius: 10px;
        overflow: hidden;
      }
      .post-card img {
        width: 100%;
        height: 220px;
        object-fit: cover;
      }
      .post-card-body {
        padding: 1.2rem;
      }
      .post-card-body h2 {
        font-size: 1rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
        line-height: 1.4;
      }
      .post-card-body h2 a {
        color: #1a4a8a;
      }
      .post-card-date {
        font-size: 0.85rem;
        color: #666;
        margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
      }
      .post-card-body p {
        font-size: 0.9rem;
        color: #444;
        line-height: 1.6;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
      }
      .read-more {
        font-size: 0.85rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        color: #1a1a1a;
        text-decoration: none;
      }
      .read-more:hover {
        color: #1a4a8a;
      }

</style>